title: A Lumberjack's Blog
description: Notes on the arboreal universe, tips on using Forestry with Gatsby.
about: This Lumberjack hails from the Pacific Northwest, specializing in fir, spruce & pine. Along with dendrology, this Lumberjack is a JAMstack aficionado. This site is built with Gatsby and the content is managed with git-backed CMS, Forestry.
